<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>candy stripe • candy striper</xh5><p> <i>candy stripe—</i>a print of fine red stripes on a white background <i>(the pattern found on peppermint candy):</i> The door was answered by a woman dressed in jeans and a <u>candy-stripe</u> shirt several sizes too big for her.</p><p><i>candy striper</i>—(U.S. sl.) a young woman who is a volunteer nurse’s aid in a hospital: Carol followed the young <u>candystriper</u> across the lobby but couldn’t keep up; her legs were still shaky.</p> </entry>
